</header>
  <div data-component="article-content">



            <p>Sega has teamed up with satnav company Waze to offer Sonic the Hedgehog voice navigation.</p>
<p>Sonic's voice is available in English or French, with the blue blur offering instructions "with his usual coolness and confidence".</p>
<p>There are also Sonic-themed icons for the Waze app, turning your car into the Speedster Lightning vehicle from the recent Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds, and you can select an "Energetic" mood to "add extra Sonic personality to your drives".</p>

<figure>
<p>
<a aria-label="Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Minecraft Pack Launch Trailer" data-platform="youtube" href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gzbMtVcJ2Ug?autoplay=1" onclick="((e) => { e.preventDefault(); e.currentTarget.closest('.video_wrapper').innerHTML = e.currentTarget.querySelector('template').innerHTML; enableElements(); })(event)" title="Click to play video from YouTube">
<span>Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Minecraft Pack Launch Trailer</span>
<template>
<iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gzbMtVcJ2Ug?autoplay=1" frameborder="0" loading="lazy" src="https://www.youtube-nocookie.com/embed/gzbMtVcJ2Ug?autoplay=1" title="Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Minecraft Pack Launch Trailer">
</iframe> </template>
</a>
</p>
<figcaption>Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds - Minecraft Pack Launch Trailer<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gzbMtVcJ2Ug" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Watch on YouTube</a></figcaption></figure>


<p>Reads the press release: "the Sonic and Waze collaboration brings more speed and fun that everyone can appreciate during their drives".</p>
<p>Just, not too much speed and fun folks, make sure you obey traffic rules!</p>
<p>This is yet another collaboration for the latest Sonic Racing game, as Sega is really on a roll here. There's a trainer and apparel <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sega-reveals-its-limited-edition-trainer-collaboration-with-puma-and-theyre-far-cooler-than-i-expected">collaboration with sports brand Puma</a>; there are <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sonic-and-shadow-coming-to-fortnite-leaks-suggest-but-not-how-youd-expect">Sonic items in Fortnite</a>; and the game itself is <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sonic-racing-crossworlds-leak-reveals-more-iconic-characters-coming-to-its-roster-which-retro-fans-will-love">filled with collaborations</a> with other brands, including Minecraft and Hatsune Miku.</p>
<p>What's more, earlier this year <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sonic-joins-mclaren-racing-in-historic-partnership-with-sega">Sega partnered with McLaren Racing</a> to become the official gaming partner of the F1 team. It's all part of Sega's Racing Around the World campaign to celebrate its latest game.</p>
<p>Sonic Racing: CrossWorlds itself is a blast, though our <a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/sonic-racing-crossworlds-review">Eurogamer review</a> admits it's "often too chaotic for its own good."</p>



